CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F423A1775920265
OL,3,CFormer detective jailed after
OL,4,Cbombarding rape victim with drunken
OL,5,Cmessages
OL,7,FA former police officer who bombarded
OL,8,Fa 14-year-old rape victim with
OL,9,Finappropriate drunken messages has
OL,10,Fbeen jailed for 18 months.
OL,12,FFormer Detective Constable John
OL,13,FHamilton, 55, sent the vulnerable girl
OL,14,Flate-night voice messages and offered
OL,15,Fto take her on a drive near where her
OL,16,Fabuser had taken her.
OL,18,FOn Friday he was jailed at Teesside
OL,19,FCrown Court after being found guilty
OL,20,Fof misconduct in a public office.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G1/13
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,424,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F423A1775920265
OL,3,CFormer detective jailed after
OL,4,Cbombarding rape victim with drunken
OL,5,Cmessages
OL,7,FJudge Francis Laird KC, the Recorder
OL,8,Fof Middlesbrough, said Hamilton had
OL,9,Fbreached the trust placed in him by a
OL,10,F"highly vulnerable" teenager who "had
OL,11,Fturned to the police for help".
OL,13,FHamilton had a 25-year policing
OL,14,Fcareer, starting with the Metropolitan
OL,15,FPolice before transferring to the
OL,16,FNorthumbria force in 2019.
OL,26,@rD@AOUrD@SO]rD@bOUsD@^O]
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G2/13
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,424,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F423A1775920265
OL,3,CFormer detective jailed after
OL,4,Cbombarding rape victim with drunken
OL,5,Cmessages
OL,7,FThe court heard that when he was
OL,8,Fassigned to the 14-year-old girl's
OL,9,Fcase in September 2021, he was "at a
OL,10,Fparticularly low ebb" and was turning
OL,11,Fto excessive drinking after separating
OL,12,Ffrom his partner.
OL,14,FHe was working with the child and
OL,15,Fadult protection safeguarding
OL,16,Fdepartment, and was asked to
OL,17,Finvestigate a historical allegation of
OL,18,Frape.
OL,26,@qD@`OUrD@UO]
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G3/13
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,424,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F423A1775920265
OL,3,CFormer detective jailed after
OL,4,Cbombarding rape victim with drunken
OL,5,Cmessages
OL,7,FThe court heard that Hamilton
OL,8,F"developed an unhealthy and entirely
OL,9,Finappropriate interest" in the victim
OL,10,Fand started to send her "increasingly
OL,11,Finappropriate messages with increasing
OL,12,Ffrequency".
OL,14,FThe judge said the messages were "over-
OL,15,Ffriendly but not overtly sexual".
OL,26,@pD@AOUqD@WO]rD@YOUtD@JO]vD@bOUwD@`O]
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G4/13
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,424,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F423A1775920265
OL,3,CFormer detective jailed after
OL,4,Cbombarding rape victim with drunken
OL,5,Cmessages
OL,7,FAfter a weekend when the girl had left
OL,8,Fher home, he made an unannounced visit
OL,9,Fto her school, and her head of year
OL,10,Fsaid Hamilton made her feel "unwelcome
OL,11,Fto remain in the room" with them,
OL,12,Fdespite the girl indicating she wished
OL,13,Fher to stay.
OL,15,FThat afternoon he messaged the girl
OL,16,Fsaying it had been good to talk to her
OL,17,Fand asked if she would like to go for
OL,18,Fa drive to a place near where her
OL,19,Fabuser had taken her.
OL,26,@rD@]OUsD@VO]
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G5/13
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,424,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F423A1775920265
OL,3,CFormer detective jailed after
OL,4,Cbombarding rape victim with drunken
OL,5,Cmessages
OL,7,FHamilton sent the girl "increasingly
OL,8,Finappropriate" messages through the
OL,9,Fnight and into the early hours of the
OL,10,Fmorning despite her making it clear
OL,11,Fshe wanted to go to bed.
OL,13,FHe also sent two voice notes revealing
OL,14,Fhe was heavily intoxicated, the court
OL,15,Fheard.
OL,17,FThe next day Hamilton tried to "undo
OL,18,Fthe damage" by sending her a series of
OL,19,Flighthearted messages, but she
OL,20,Freported what had happened at school.
OL,26,@oD@XOUpD@NO]yD@`OUzD@KO]
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G6/13
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,424,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42307
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F423A1775920265
OL,3,CFormer detective jailed after
OL,4,Cbombarding rape victim with drunken
OL,5,Cmessages
OL,7,FThe girl's head of year said the girl
OL,8,Fwas "visibly upset and saying she
OL,9,Fdidn't want to go on this drive".
OL,11,FIn mitigation, the court heard
OL,12,FHamilton's messages were "pestering"
OL,13,Fbut not "sexual, threatening or
OL,14,Fobscene".
OL,16,FThe Independent Office for Police
OL,17,FConduct (IOPC) started a criminal
OL,18,Finvestigation into Hamilton in
OL,19,FNovember 2021 after a referral from
OL,20,FNorthumbria Police.
OL,26,@pD@EOUqD@`O]tD@ZOUtD@dO]uD@IOUvD@HO]
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G7/13
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,424,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42308
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F423A1775920265
OL,3,CFormer detective jailed after
OL,4,Cbombarding rape victim with drunken
OL,5,Cmessages
OL,7,FHe was suspended by the force and
OL,8,Farrested by the IOPC later that month.
OL,10,FThe IOPC said it concluded its
OL,11,Finvestigation in February 2023 and
OL,12,Freferred a file of evidence to the
OL,13,FCrown Prosecution Service.
OL,15,FHamilton was charged in August 2024
OL,16,Fand went on trial in February this
OL,17,Fyear.
OL,19,FHe will face a gross misconduct
OL,20,Fhearing after his conviction.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G8/13
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,424,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42309
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F423A1775920265
OL,3,CFormer detective jailed after
OL,4,Cbombarding rape victim with drunken
OL,5,Cmessages
OL,7,FIOPC director Emily Barry said: "DC
OL,8,FHamilton was an experienced police
OL,9,Fofficer with over 24 years of service
OL,10,Fso he knew perfectly well the
OL,11,Fstandards of professional behaviour
OL,12,Fexpected of him, whether on or off
OL,13,Fduty.
OL,15,F"The seriousness of his actions were
OL,16,Fexacerbated by the fact he worked in a
OL,17,Fsafeguarding team and was meant to be
OL,18,Fprotecting a 14-year-old girl who was
OL,19,Fin an extremely vulnerable position as
OL,20,Fa victim of crime.
OL,26,@oD@aOUwD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G9/13
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,424,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42310
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F423A1775920265
OL,3,CFormer detective jailed after
OL,4,Cbombarding rape victim with drunken
OL,5,Cmessages
OL,7,F"Police officers are made fully aware
OL,8,Ffrom the outset of their
OL,9,Fresponsibilities with how they deal
OL,10,Fwith members of the public they meet
OL,11,Fthrough their professional duties.
OL,12,FHamilton completely abused his
OL,13,Fposition of trust and has rightfully
OL,14,Fbeen held accountable for his actions."
OL,16,FDetective Superintendent Donna Rose,
OL,17,Ffrom Northumbria Police's Professional
OL,18,FStandards Department, said: "Firstly,
OL,19,Fwe want to recognise the bravery of
OL,20,Fthe victim in this case in coming
OL,21,Fforward.
OL,26,@oD@AOUvD@gO]zD@]OU
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}       G10/13
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,424,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42311
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F423A1775920265
OL,3,CFormer detective jailed after
OL,4,Cbombarding rape victim with drunken
OL,5,Cmessages
OL,7,F"When concerns were raised in relation
OL,8,Fto this individual he was suspended
OL,9,Ffrom duty.
OL,11,F"The case was referred to the
OL,12,FIndependent Office for Police Conduct
OL,13,F(IOPC) who conducted an investigation,
OL,14,Fduring the course of which he retired.
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}       G11/13
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,424,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42312
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F423A1775920265
OL,3,CFormer detective jailed after
OL,4,Cbombarding rape victim with drunken
OL,5,Cmessages
OL,7,F"His actions were completely
OL,8,Funacceptable and are in no way
OL,9,Frepresentative of the overwhelming
OL,10,Fmajority of officers, staff and
OL,11,Fvolunteers at Northumbria Police who
OL,12,Fcome to work to make a positive
OL,13,Fdifference to people's lives.
OL,15,F"As a force, we have made it very
OL,16,Fclear that when someone falls below
OL,17,Fthe standards expected and which they
OL,18,Fmade a commitment to uphold we will
OL,19,Ftake appropriate action.
OL,26,@oD@AOUwD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}       G12/13
